{"tid":406584,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"自我介紹 誠招女友","createTime":"2017-09-19T18:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T04:29:01.000Z","uid":49903,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a78dfe1931e2543e164995dbaa5a4866a77e20b","tid":406584,"uid":49903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T18:12:27.000Z","msg":"本人22歲<br />\n<br />\n中六畢業 差不多全部u<br />\n跟住走去讀左兩三年ive<br />\nHighdip畢業<br />\n依家做緊電工學徒<br />\n月入15k左右<br />\n住公屋<br />\n<br />\n冇特別興趣<br />\n打機 篤波<br />\n同fd 吹水 hea<br />\n依排學緊整甜品<br />\n<br />\n食煙<br />\n唔飲酒<br />\n有粗口 （視乎場合）<br />\n唔叫雞<br />\n<br />\n爛面(冇得救）<br />\n有白頭髮<br />\nJ短<br />\n快射<br />\n粗眉<br />\n1米71<br />\n瘦底<br />\n依排有做gym<br />\n唔靚仔<br />\n應該未去到樣衰<br />\n不過皮膚差 所以影響到個樣 接近樣衰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己唔算大洗<br />\n願意洗錢落你身上 （應該）<br />\n專一（掛）<br />\n想結婚生細路（能力許可的話）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n短期目標<br />\n1盡力搵最多既錢<br />\n2整到好味既甜品<br />\n<br />\n中期目標<br />\n1儲50萬 3至4年內<br />\n2電工師傅<br />\n3整到好味而又靚既甜品<br />\n<br />\n長期目標（盡力而為）<br />\n1開一間甜品鋪仔<br />\n2上車<br />\n3擁有一個幸福既小家庭<br />\n<br />\n基本介紹係咁上下 <br />\n不過始終都係文字介紹 <br />\n要相處一段子日先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19493e7fc41867a3e4849e76157b4fd52d9780f5","tid":406584,"uid":130673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T18:25:19.000Z","msg":"$300/h 唔過夜，洗費你比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c05be6ea54f73d48b77bbfd0e8c64aadab486ad","tid":406584,"uid":2419,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T18:28:29.000Z","msg":"嘩 d女俾你溝撚晒啦"},{"pid":"4fe0125b126d2ae87f4f9808144769a1f9ee8a8b","tid":406584,"uid":10608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T18:47:26.000Z","msg":"你仲夠膽出街？"},{"pid":"e11e37ad918599d491baee1c33732baa40b9d129","tid":406584,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T18:55:30.000Z","msg":"人生贏家"},{"pid":"2ee3b9713b1e71726403ef4f1a617cacb0136ad7","tid":406584,"uid